ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 214, Saskatchewan
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 214 declares the wildfires that occurred in Saskatchewan from August 15, 2017 until September 16, 2017, to be of concern to the federal government and authorizes the Minister to provide financial assistance to the province of SASKATCHEWAN.
